235
00:13:48,497 --> 00:13:49,264
you notice that?

236
00:13:49,798 --> 00:13:52,100
[Rui Prieto] Yeah. Yeah. The,
the water is becoming clearer.

237
00:13:52,135 --> 00:13:53,868
[James Cameron]
No luck this time,

238
